013package org.apache.juneau.plaintext.annotation;
014
015import org.apache.juneau.*;
016import org.apache.juneau.plaintext.*;
017import org.apache.juneau.reflect.*;
018import org.apache.juneau.svl.*;
019
020/**
021 * Utility classes and methods for the {@link PlainTextConfig @PlainTextConfig} annotation.
022 *
023 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
024 * </ul>
025 */
026public class PlainTextConfigAnnotation {
027
028   /**
029    * Applies {@link PlainTextConfig} annotations to a {@link org.apache.juneau.plaintext.PlainTextSerializer.Builder}.
030    */
031   public static class SerializerApply extends AnnotationApplier<PlainTextConfig,PlainTextSerializer.Builder> {
032
033      /**
034       * Constructor.
035       *
036       * @param vr The resolver for resolving values in annotations.
037       */
038      public SerializerApply(VarResolverSession vr) {
039         super(PlainTextConfig.class, PlainTextSerializer.Builder.class, vr);
040      }
041
042      @Override
043      public void apply(AnnotationInfo<PlainTextConfig> ai, PlainTextSerializer.Builder b) {
044      }
045   }
046
047   /**
048    * Applies {@link PlainTextConfig} annotations to a {@link org.apache.juneau.plaintext.PlainTextParser.Builder}.
049    */
050   public static class ParserApply extends AnnotationApplier<PlainTextConfig,PlainTextParser.Builder> {
051
052      /**
053       * Constructor.
054       *
055       * @param vr The resolver for resolving values in annotations.
056       */
057      public ParserApply(VarResolverSession vr) {
058         super(PlainTextConfig.class, PlainTextParser.Builder.class, vr);
059      }
060
061      @Override
062      public void apply(AnnotationInfo<PlainTextConfig> ai, PlainTextParser.Builder b) {
063      }
064   }
065}
